  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wearables/\" rel=\"tag\">佩戴产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/27/samsung-exec-confirms-gal-gear-note-iii-ifa/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/08/galnote3.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n之前除了极具暗示意味的邀请函和一些流言之外，并没有直接的证据可以证明 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/27/samsung-galaxy-note-iii-rumor-4k-video-recording/\">Galaxy Note III</a> 和 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/06/samsung-galaxy-gear-smartwatch-trademark/\">Galaxy Gear</a> 将会在 9 月 4 日的发表会上亮相。直到今天，三星移动副总裁李永熙（Lee Young-hee）在接受 <a href=\"http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/tech/2013/08/133_141776.html\">Korea Times</a> 采访时终于证实了这一说法。除此之外，他还透露 Galaxy Gear（之前被称作概念可穿戴装置）并不会采用<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/flexibledisplay\">可弯曲屏幕</a>，同时表示它将是一款需搭配智能手机使用的产品。关于新手机的内容则没有被提到太多，但没关系，<a href=\"http://translate.google.com/translate?sl=auto&amp;tl=en&amp;js=n&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=en&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fsamsung.hdblog.it%2F2013%2F08%2F27%2Fed-ecco-a-voi-il-samsung-galaxy-note-3%2F\">HD Blog</a> 已经为大家找来了其正面面板的谍照，想看完整图集的话就去第二个引用来源瞧瞧吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/08/27/samsung-exec-confirms-gal-gear-note-iii-ifa/\">Engadget</a>、<a href=\"http://www.sammobile.com/2013/08/27/samsung-exec-confirms-september-4th-unveiling-of-galaxy-note-iii-and-galaxy-gear/#.UhxsQhSRgZU.twitter\" target=\"_blank\">SamMobile</a>、<a href=\"http://sonnydickson.com/2013/08/27/hands-on-with-the-samsung-galaxy-note-3/\" target=\"_blank\">Sonny Dickson</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/tech/2013/08/133_141776.html\" target=\"_blank\">Korea Times</a>、<a href=\"http://translate.google.com/translate?sl=auto&amp;tl=en&amp;js=n&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=en&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fsamsung.hdblog.it%2F2013%2F08%2F27%2Fed-ecco-a-voi-il-samsung-galaxy-note-3%2F\" target=\"_blank\">HD Blog (翻译)</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/27/samsung-exec-confirms-gal-gear-note-iii-ifa/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20704442/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/08/27/samsung-exec-confirms-gal-gear-note-iii-ifa/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
